text: Got some Pink Lady apples from the Farmer's Market and Dr. Healey was right in one of his tangents. These are the best darn apples ever.
Honey Crisp is the way to go.
Ladies and Gentleman, I present to you the next big thing in the apple world -The Cosmic Crisp. <http://www.cosmiccrisp.com/the-facts/>

attachments.title: The Facts
attachments.text: Cosmic Crisp™ brand apples web center. Learn about the large, juicy apple's remarkably firm and crisp texture with an exceptional flavor profile that provides ample sweetness and tartness, making it an excellent eating apple. In addition to being delicious, it is slow to brown when cut and maintains its texture and flavor in storage for more than a year.

attachments.text: Today on the show, how we got from mealy, nasty apples to apples that taste delicious. The story starts with a breeder who discovered a miracle apple. But discovering that apple wasn't enough.
